![Episode107.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578271674918-QP6SMEIDW4F9VU8IFQYG/Episode107.jpg)

Goodbye 2019! Hello 2020! Dust off that ol' crystal ball and join us in looking forward and seeing what this new year has to offer! Will Spidey join Eddie and Cletus in Venom 2? What role is Steve Trevor playing in Wonder Woman 1984? Is ANYONE excited for Morbius?! These questions and more will be answered on this super breezy episode of the Major Issue Podcast!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

